erage added for:\n- JAXB marshalling/unmarshalling of annotated object graphs\n- `@XmlID` / `@XmlIDREF`\n- `XmlAdapter` for `LocalDate`\n- Field-based JAXB access and lifecycle callbacks\n- Polymorphic element lists with `@XmlElements`\n- Map adaptation through `XmlAdapter`\n- DOM updates through `Binder`\n- Schema generation and schema-backed unmarshalling\n\nNo build files or metadata/config files were modified. Per instruction, I did not compile or run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03e12e815af3fdff0169ff04ff0c1081a0892a8d9bb5497a0c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3038, "output": 1436, "cacheRead": 26624, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 31098, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778320619542, "responseId": "resp_03e12e815af3fdff0169ff04ec2abc81a0afb2f2b4402b0a6f"}, "toolResults": []}
